stsbl-iserv-sftp (17.06.29-0) experimental; urgency=medium

  [ Felix Jacobi ]
  * Added umask to sftp options.
  * Apply command line options also to ForceCommand directives as global 
    options seems to does not have any effect.
  * Removed global command restrictions and umask to allow root still 
    to use symlinks and keep his restrictive umask.
  * Use special sftp subsystem command with umask junction for users
    with shell.
